***Disk Queta Management(DQM)**

a. softlimit=warning

b. hardlimit=restriction


1. rpm -qa quota or yum check quata.

2. mkfs.ext4 /dev/block-device-name 

3. mkdir /dir

4. make entry in /etc/fstab

5. mount /dev/block-device-name /dir

6. make usrquota,grpquota beside defaults option in fstab of /dev/block-device-name

7. 

